ai.grakn.util

Enum ErrorMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ErrorMessage>
      • ai.grakn.util.ErrorMessage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<ErrorMessage>

    public enum ErrorMessage
extends Enum<ErrorMessage>
    Enum containing error messages. Each error message contains a single format string, with a method getMessage(Object...) that accepts arguments to be passed to the format string.
    Author:
    Filipe Teixeira
